t67\">: most </span><span class=\"Latn\" lang=\"en\" about=\"#mwt67\"><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/well#English\" title=\"well\">well</a></span></p><ul><li>A popular aphorism says it <b>best</b><span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">:</span> A bird in the hand is worth two in the bush.</li></ul></div>", "<div class=\"definition\"><p>To the most advantage; with the most success, cause, profit, benefit, or propriety.</p><ul><li>You\'d <b>best</b> save a backup copy, just in case the morons lose the one that you sent and then try to act like you never sent one.</li></ul></div>", "<div class=\"definition\"><p><span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt94\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> The supreme effort one can make, or has made.</p><ul><li>I did my <b>best</b>.</li><li>My personal <b>best</b> in that race is eighteen minutes, four seconds.</li></ul></div>", "<div class=\"definition\"><p><span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt98\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> One\'s best <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/behavior\" title=\"behavior\">behavior</a>.</p><ul><li>I was somewhat distant lately, and my lady promised me head every Tuesday of the week when I’m nice to her, so I better be on my <b>best</b>.</li></ul></div>", "<div class=\"definition\"><p><span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt100\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> The person (or persons; or thing or things) that is (are) most <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/excellent\" title=\"excellent\">excellent</a>.</p><ul><li>Even the <b>best</b> of us makes mistakes.</li><li>We\'re the <b>best</b> of friends.</li><li>I love it so much<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">!</span> It\'s the <b>best</b>.</li></ul></div>", "<div class=\"definition\"><p><span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt154\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> To <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/surpass\" title=\"surpass\">surpass</a> in <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/skill\" title=\"skill\">skill</a> or <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/achievement\" title=\"achievement\">achievement</a>.</p><ul></ul></div>", "<div class=\"definition\"><p><span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt155\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> To <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/beat\" title=\"beat\">beat</a> in a contest.</p><ul></ul></div>", "<div class=\"definition\"><p><span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt204\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/had_best\" title=\"had best\">Had best</a>.</p><ul><li>It\'s getting late. You <b>best</b> get on home.</li></ul></div>"]
